Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:22.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:22.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:28.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
