Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:32.31,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
